SUMMARY:Winters Art and Wine Festival
DESCRIPTION:The Yolo County Vineyard and Winery Association invites you to our annual Winters Art & Wine Festival on Saturday\, May 2nd from 12 – 4 PM. Join us in Downtown Winters for an afternoon of art & wine.\nPlein air artists\, local and regional artist booths\, wine tasting from the Yolo Wines wineries\, and music by The Charlie Wade Blues Band\nThe event will feature 30 Plein Air Artists painting throughout Yolo County and featuring their freshly painted work at the Art & Wine Festival alongside more than a dozen local and regional artists showcasing their work. Enjoy a fun day with award-winning wines from the Yolo Wines wineries\, plus art\, and live music!\nThe art exhibits are FREE for public viewing. The wine tasting ticket is $45 and includes tastings from all participating Yolo wineries throughout the event.\nThis event will feature our Yolo Wines Wineries & tastes of their award-winning and estate-grown wines. Register for the wine tasting and find more information on the website.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/winters-art-wine-festival/
LOCATION:Downtown Winters\, Main Street\, Winters\, CA\, 95694\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2026-04-21-085154.png
END:VEVENT
