SUMMARY:Build a Bouquet at The HIVE
DESCRIPTION:Create your unique expression of the season. Pollinator Garden Educator and Steward\, Rowan Boswell\, and Nectar Director Josh Zeldner will share knowledge about the plants we will be using\, exclusively from The HIVE’s Pollinator Habitat. Explore aromatic blossoms and branches to build a not-so-typical bouquet.\n\nTickets at https://thehivewoodland.com/event/build-a-bouqet/
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/build-a-bouquet-at-the-hive/
LOCATION:The HIVE / Z Specialty Food\, The HIVE Tasting Room and Kitchen
